{"tid":1333860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試下唔好再叫佢地做\"建制派\", 試下叫\"權貴\"","createTime":"2019-07-20T01:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T09:33:22.000Z","uid":75664,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e63a6db2c30a0f21e2c8241ec0167f9a6d5d2eff","tid":1333860,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"地產商就叫番<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">奸商</span></span><br />\n藍絲，警察，就叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">權貴走狗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黃絲就叫番<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人民，平民百姓</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點評時下局勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332538</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇左依個好post 話 Rebranding 好緊要，因為依家用緊d 名其實有啲誤導成份，令到普羅大眾有錯覺直觀認為政府建制代表繁榮，穩定，法治，而黃絲泛民就代表反叛，不合法，動亂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以大家請今日開始改口！！！"},{"pid":"169d4686ff9693cd91fdbcf4daf4bb7e694d9407","tid":1333860,"uid":31237,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:35:48.000Z","msg":"邊忽貴<br />\n親北京/親中派就得"},{"pid":"45c91184ada6339e209f7309ccc4acd8b2d7700e","tid":1333860,"uid":75664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:36:06.000Z","msg":"全部稱呼都無詆毁，亦係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7d73bd1046287ee0a6b08cce0b662c65da6308","tid":1333860,"uid":20880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:36:39.000Z","msg":"舐共派"},{"pid":"ec223f7ef587cdc16e3f3ab940a7b33c41a7fc02","tid":1333860,"uid":75664,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"169d4686ff9693cd91fdbcf4daf4bb7e694d9407","tid":1333860,"uid":31237,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:35:48.000Z","msg":"邊忽貴<br />\n親北京/親中派就得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T01:37:13.000Z","msg":"你叫親中派咁愛國藍絲咪仲攬佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\